{
  "stem": "734.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But you can simply take it for granted that anything-- they did away with everything that would be of benefit to us, no matter what, little, stupid items, to a point where you had to get off the sidewalk when you encountered a German in uniform-- tip your cap, take off your hat, get off the sidewalk, walk around them.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And if you hadn't, if you didn't-- and they really, ah, they had so many ways to get back at you.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I mean, would kick the heck out of you on the spot, which I've seen many times happen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because a lot of Jews simply were not aware of all the rules, regulations.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Or maybe they didn't think of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Or maybe they didn't think they should do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So they [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] didn't pay attention.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then when you didn't pay attention, you really-- you learned it the, the hard way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "No transportation for Jews-- you could not own a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This, I remember-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I remember a time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "This was before the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "This must have been in late '39, in the winter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Somebody we knew thought that he could get away and keep his bike.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they shot him once while he was driving that bike.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He was shot on-- while he was riding that bike down the street a few blocks away from us, German cop, gendarme.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Without any warning or anything-- they just realized that the guy was violating a rule.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He is not supposed to ride a bike.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And of course, they knew he was doing it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Because he had the armband on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So took an aim and shot him riding on the bike.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
